<p>Intertwingly.net is moving to <a href="http://dreamhost.com/">DreamHost</a>.  I’m sure that every one of my scripts has hard coded paths or depend on the server being in EST/EDT or will otherwise break for unanticipated (but in retrospect entirely obvious) reasons.  I don’t believe that I will lose any email in the process, but you never know.</p>
<p>My <code>@apache.org</code> email address will not be affected by this move.</p></div></content>
